cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on spoken language understanding and proposes a method for integrating dialogue history into an end-to-end SLU system. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech signals and their processing. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a neural network model for SLU and evaluates different types of embeddings. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply as the paper deals with machine learning techniques for natural language processing. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category, but could apply as the paper deals with dialogue history and its representation in SLU systems.
